channel.title: How do i fix disabled skills
channel.description: I downloaded a client and source and when i was testing all the skills I saw that Firemaking was disable. And when i tried to burn up a log, I got a message that said "Firemaking is disable". And i just want to know how i fix it and enable it.

item.title: How do i fix disabled skills
item.dc:creator: @Loveandpower Loveandpower
item.description:
@Loveandpower wrote:

[quote=“voetbal645, post:2, topic:518786”]Just try to search for the message in the source, it’s probably disabled for a reason.
So you probably need to fix up firemaking to.[/quote]^

places you may want to try…

-itemonitem
-firemaking skill file/folder
-actionhandler
-clickitem packet
-useitem

there are several files it could be in lol
